<rml>
<head>
	<title>Gas Quest</title>
	<link type="text/rcss" href="GasQuestWidget.rcss"/>
</head>
<body>
	<div id="quest-root">
		<div id="quest-panel">
			<div class="quest-badge">QUEST 02</div>
			<div class="quest-title">주유하기</div>
			<div class="quest-body">GasStation으로 이동해 주유를 완료하세요.</div>
			<button id="gas-quest-ok-button" class="quest-button">Okay</button>
		</div>
	</div>
</body>
</rml>
